    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Yeah, a bit bummed about it actually. It's gonna be a massive change. Like, we were just getting into some really heavy, deep stuff with the protagonist's arc, and now it's all gonna be... sanitized. The template basically limits your ability to explore any conflict that isn't super surface-level. I'm worried the books are gonna feel really hollow. Don't you think the quality is gonna take a massive hit if we can't do the complex stuff anymore?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
